{"tid":1269163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"現在是6月30日 夜晚9:15 ，香港人，全體集結立法會煲底！！！！！","createTime":"2019-06-30T13:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T13:29:30.000Z","uid":168161,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"125897ee18933e03db43951902ffd7644011730d","tid":1269163,"uid":168161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:15:26.000Z","msg":"呢場運動已經接近尾聲。<br />\n7月1日 係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最後一個機會</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n我由6月9日開始 次次野餐 <strong>無一次缺席</strong>，<br />\n每次行動過後 返到屋企 睇住部電視，<br />\n我地嘅行動 出黎嘅手足 一次比一次少人，<br />\n由612 響徹雲霄嘅「撤回！」「撤回！」<br />\n到最近嘅包圍律政司、保衛海濱，<br />\n行動<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">影響力已經越來越小</span></strong>。<br />\n好多身邊朋友 意志唔夠堅決 開始心淡......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦有人頂唔順頻繁出動，漸覺體力不支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<strong>真係好攰，出少我一個......唔緊要啦......</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母！快撚d出黎啦！多你一個參與， 就係勝利嘅關鍵！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n出黎啦！自由閪們！<br />\n<br />\n即使得孤身一個 即使身心疲憊不堪，<br />\n求下你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今晚一定要出黎。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>以一身傲骨，承先烈之碧血</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n各位 煲底見！"},{"pid":"9d30ffef16b6d7c745745baecc043f41df8bbc43","tid":1269163,"uid":269997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:17:15.000Z","msg":"係現場啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2acb99270560aac440ab36adb78a17730379317f","tid":1269163,"uid":221202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:17:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"529a2fab3eed834a2b2110d67231764